    stable 2.2.2 2.2.1 2.2 2.1 2.0
   require libvorbis
  optional libtheora '' '' for theora video codex support
  optional speex     '' '' for speex voice codex support
     ignore ''2003''
  category audio/library
 attribute library
    source http://downloads.xiph.org/releases/libshout/libshout-$VERSION.tar.gz
  homepage http://www.icecast.org/
      opts --enable-static
  estimate 500
      desc 'libshout is a library for communicating with icecast streaming media servers.

libshout allows applications to easily communicate
and broadcast to an Icecast streaming media server.
It handles the socket connections, metadata communication,
and data streaming for the calling application,
and lets developers focus on feature sets instead
of implementation details.'
